headline.main: Foster Doesn't Appeared Worried About Combine Ejection
headline.print_headline: Foster Doesn't Appeared Worried About Combine Ejection

lead_paragraph: If linebacker Reuben Foster is worried that he hurt his draft stock by getting kicked out of the NFL's scouting combine he isn't showing it.
